query:
SELECT
                            idx as "index: _",
                            value as "value: _"
                        FROM historical_slots
                        WHERE account_address = $1
                        AND idx = $2
                        AND block_number = (SELECT MAX(block_number)
                                                FROM historical_slots
                                                WHERE account_address = $1
                                                AND idx = $2
                                                AND block_number <= $3)
